column20: What type of careers are there for computer programmers?
column23:
1)  As a software developer in our company you will be a part of a team that develops the next generation technologies.



2) They turn the program designs created by software developers and engineers into instructions that a computer can follow.



3) Programmers must debug the programs—that is, test them to ensure that they produce the expected results.



4) Computer programmers typically do the following: Write programs in a variety of computer languages, such as C, C++ ,C# , python, and in variety of fields like Cryptography, artificial intelligence (AI), Internet networking ,  computer graphics and operating systems.

Find "reasonable" dieting advice, that is not fads or medications
    but reasonable methods for weight loss.
column23:
1)  Do you think you need a diet?



2) first, Check your Body Mass Index (BMI) - an indicator of body fat - and see where it fits within the BMI categories.



3) If you found out you are overweight or obese, discuss weight loss with your doctor and decide on a goal.



4) If you have a lot of weight to lose, set a realistic intermediate goal, maybe to lose 10 pounds or aim yourself a size.



5) Remember that even a small amount of weight loss can lead to big health benefits.



6) Estimate your calorie needs.



7) You might feel less confident and even a bit sluggish.



8) Another fast things you can do - drink more water and avoid liquid calories, take a "before" picture, put aside leftovers,Remember!



9) Diet is not just what you eat!



10) Try adding exercise to your daily routine!

column20:
Find information on French Lick Resort and Casino in
  Indiana.
column23:
1)  French Lick Resort stands out among Midwest hotels for its AAA Four-Diamond accommodations and for the charm of its staff.



2) Nestled in the Indiana countryside, the winner of the 2015 USA Today 10Best Readers' Choice Award for Best Historic Hotel is both a breath of fresh air and an exciting family adventure.



3) The beautifully restored historic French Lick Springs Hotel and West Baden Springs Hotel capture the opulence of times long past, and ensure an escape from the norm for everyone who visits.



4) An easy drive from Indianapolis and Louisville, this upscale destination features championship golf courses, world-class spas, Vegas-style gaming, horseback riding and activities for kids.



5) Family-friendly activities and facilities make this an ideal destination for celebrations or relaxing getaways.

column23:

2) VoIP involves sending voice information in digital form in discrete packets rather than by using the traditional circuit-committed protocols of the public switched telephone network.



3) A major advantage of VoIP and Internet telephony is that it avoids the tolls charged by ordinary telephone service.

column20: Find information on Barbados history.
column23:
1)    The island of Barbados is located at 13.4ºN and 54.4ºW and is situated in the western area of the North Atlantic Ocean.



2) The peaceful Arawaks and the Caribs were the first inhabitants of Barbados.



3) However, when English Captain, John Powell arrived in 1625, the island was uninhabited and as a result he claimed it for King James I of England.



4) Coral reefs fringe the Barbados shoreline to provide excellent snorkeling and Scuba Diving.

column23:
1) Not sure how to quit smoking cigarettes?


2) Try one of these 20+ ways to stop smoking and start your path towards a healthier, smoke-free life.


3) Make an honest list of all the things you like about smoking.


4) Draw a line down the center of a piece of paper and write them on one side; on the other side make a list of all the things you dislike, such as how it can interfere with your health, work, family, etc., suggests Daniel Z. Lieberman, M.D., director of the Clinical Psychiatric Research Center at George Washington University Medical Center in Washington, D.C.


5) Started earnest brother believe an exposed so


6) If you are brave enough, get feedback from family and friends about things they donate like about your use of cigarettes.


7) When the negative side outweighs the positive side, you are ready to quit.

1) Can condo dwellers still have it all while living small?
